parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the auto park brake system can cause the vehicle to suddenly engage the parking brake, leading to a loss of control, accidents, or injuries.
symptoms: The auto park light and brake light come on simultaneously
a strong burning smell is present
the vehicle suddenly stops or slows down without warning
the parking brake engages randomly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the windshield can cause reduced visibility, increased risk of injury, and potential ejection from the vehicle in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The windshield pops out or shatters
the windshield buckles or breaks
the windshield wiper fails
obstructing the driver's view.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the windshield wiper can reduce visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially during inclement weather conditions.
symptoms: The windshield wiper fails to operate
the windshield wiper leaves streaks or residue on the windshield
the windshield wiper makes unusual noises or vibrations.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The incorrect wiring of the lavatory fan can cause harmful fumes to be blown inside the motorhome, posing a health risk to occupants.
symptoms: Fumes or odors are present inside the motorhome
the lavatory fan is not functioning properly
the fan is blowing air inside instead of outside.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the ignition to come out in the driver's hand, leading to loss of vehicle control and potential accidents.
symptoms: The ignition switch feels loose or wobbly
the ignition key comes out while driving
the vehicle stalls or loses power while in motion.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the slide-out seal can cause water to enter the vehicle, leading to damage to the interior, electrical systems, and potentially causing mold and mildew growth, which can lead to health issues and reduce the overall safety and habitability of the vehicle.
symptoms: Water leaks into the vehicle when the slide-out is opened
water damage to the interior
visible gaps or openings between the slide-out and the vehicle body
water accumulation in the storage areas.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The water leak in the storage area can cause damage to stored items, corrosion to metal components, and potentially lead to electrical system failures, which can cause safety hazards and reduce the overall reliability of the vehicle.
symptoms: Water accumulation in the storage area
water damage to stored items
corrosion or rust on metal components
musty or mildew odor in the storage area.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the hydraulic jack lines can cause them to fall off and get tangled in the front tire, resulting in damage to the wheel and potentially leading to loss of control or accidents.
symptoms: Hydraulic jack lines fall off
get tangled in the front tire
damage to the wheel.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the slide-out unit can cause it to fall off while traveling, potentially leading to accidents or damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: Slide-out unit falls off while traveling
defective seals.
